quoteText: If any part of these terms shall be deemed invalid or unenforceable that part shall be replaced by a valid, enforceable term that comes closest to the intended meaning and leave the remainder of these terms unaffected.
title: Invalidity of any portion of the Terms of Service does not entail invalidity of its remainder
